The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 No training on Berlin pitch

Berlin: France and Italy cannot train at the Olympiastadion before Sundays final because of the condition of the pitch, Fifa said on Friday. A spokesman confirmed that Fifa had taken the decision because of the state of the pitch and heavy rainfall in Berlin over the last couple of days. (Reuters) 




